       <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will continue to support enhanced the audit capacity of the OAG through strengthening the audit tools, fundamental changing environment of audit concepts and principles and upgrading the skills and knowledge of auditors migrated to technology driven accounting procedures and equip them with technological tools</narrative>
      </comment>
     </target>
     <actual>
      <comment>
       <narrative xml:lang="EN"></narrative>
      </comment>
     </actual>
    </period>
